Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.11,0:00:06.59,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Is the data accurate?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:09.23,Gatchaman-Main,Pman,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Although I don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:15.50,Gatchaman-Main,Pman,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then, MESS has stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.50,0:00:17.72,Gatchaman-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,all harmful activity \Ntoward human society.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:20.40,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Ohhh... Is this a reaction, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:22.04,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me! You love origami, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.38,0:00:26.39,Gatchaman-Main,Pman,0000,0000,0000,,All the absorbed humans have \Nbeen safely returned, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:27.71,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:29.74,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,That's way too awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.74,0:00:31.34,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Case closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:33.70,Gatchaman-Main,Pman,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let down our guard just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:35.26,Gatchaman-Main,Pman,0000,0000,0000,,They just stopped {\i1}doing{\i0} anything;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:37.05,Gatchaman-Main,Pman,0000,0000,0000,,they haven't stopped \Nmaking an appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.43,0:00:41.52,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, can't you just \Nbe happy, Pai-Pai?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:43.23,Gatchaman-Main,Pman,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me Pai-Pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:46.08,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, do you prefer Pai-san, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:48.48,Gatchaman-Main,Pman,0000,0000,0000,,You're messing with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.68,0:00:54.00,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying that no one's \Nbeen abducted since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:56.82,Gatchaman-Main,Pman,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. No one since.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:00:59.99,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:01.94,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Not "What?"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.94,0:01:04.54,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you do to it back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.87,0:01:07.24,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought I'd make it cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.82,0:01:12.21,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, doesn't it seem like it's \Ncommunicating with Hajime-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:14.80,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's MESSY-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:17.68,Gatchaman-Main,Pman,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you introducing it to us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:19.69,Gatchaman-Main,Pman,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, don't even name it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.69,0:01:22.01,Gatchaman-Main,Pman,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way anyone can \Ncommunicate with a MESS...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.38,0:01:27.87,Gatchaman-Main,Pman,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.87,0:01:30.11,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Its shape-changing might have \Nsomething to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:33.24,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we collaborated with our scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.24,0:01:35.61,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.06,0:01:40.36,Gatchaman-Main,Jou,0000,0000,0000,,Change the body's shape \Nto exchange information, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:42.62,Gatchaman-Main,Jou,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's how \Nthey communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:44.66,Gatchaman-Main,Pman,0000,0000,0000,,That's way too far-fetched!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:46.18,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,But, it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:49.28,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Why did all the MESS act \Nas one, at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:52.39,Gatchaman-Main,Jou,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they can share information.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:53.63,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:55.98,Gatchaman-Main,Jou,0000,0000,0000,,So, just like with this NOTE,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.98,0:01:58.26,Gatchaman-Main,Jou,0000,0000,0000,,information might be \Ntransmitted instantaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:02:01.97,Gatchaman-Main,Jou,0000,0000,0000,,They might be a life \Nform with a hive mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.75,0:02:04.95,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,That's kind of sexy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:06.28,Gatchaman-Main,Pman,0000,0000,0000,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:07.26,Gatchaman-Main,Pman,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.26,0:02:09.51,Gatchaman-Main,Pman,0000,0000,0000,,My orders were to exterminate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.51,0:02:12.40,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,But when we try \Nto catch it, it vanishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:13.73,Gatchaman-Main,Pman,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:26.74,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:29.97,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe MESS-chan never had any animosity \Ntoward us in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.97,0:02:32.77,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,and just didn't realize \Nwe were around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:34.17,Gatchaman-Main,Pman,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:35.86,Gatchaman-Main,Pman,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:38.59,Gatchaman-Main,Pman,0000,0000,0000,,They've clearly been doing \Nharm until recently!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:42.05,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,"Oh, no! I've stepped on an ant!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.74,0:02:44.23,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:49.14,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Even a philanthropist like me might \Ndo that while I'm walking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:51.57,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:54.55,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,From their perspective, \Nwe're like ants?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:56.77,Gatchaman-Main,Jou,0000,0000,0000,,Ants might be giving \Nus a lot of credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:59.15,Gatchaman-Main,Jou,0000,0000,0000,,Might be more like rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:01.53,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Way too sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:03.12,Gatchaman-Main,Utsutsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dreamy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:07.83,Gatchaman-Main,Pman,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then, what we've been \Ndoing until now is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:09.50,Gatchaman-Main,Jou,0000,0000,0000,,A waste, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.69,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,That's being way too harsh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:13.47,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,But it's spot-on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:17.30,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's true that \Nwe did save people...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:20.17,Gatchaman-Main,Jou,0000,0000,0000,,Well, compared to our \NGatchaman predecessors,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:21.68,Gatchaman-Main,Jou,0000,0000,0000,,we're pathetic enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:27.85,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, now my shoulders are tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:30.74,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Please keep it together, Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:35.69,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:38.78,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give this to you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:40.11,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:44.27,Gatchaman-Main,Utsutsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dreamy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:11.04,Gatchaman-Main,AvatarB,0000,0000,0000,,That's a troublesome neighbor \Nyou've got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:14.83,Gatchaman-Main,AvatarA,0000,0000,0000,,We have a baby, \Nso, of course, the baby will cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:16.76,Gatchaman-Main,AvatarA,0000,0000,0000,,But the neighbor says \Nwe're being too loud
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:19.15,Gatchaman-Main,AvatarA,0000,0000,0000,,and playing music with \Nthe volume cranked way up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:22.36,Gatchaman-Main,AvatarC,0000,0000,0000,,They might both be unwanted noise,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:24.30,Gatchaman-Main,AvatarC,0000,0000,0000,,but for entirely different reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:26.84,Gatchaman-Main,AvatarA,0000,0000,0000,,Things have escalated recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:29.22,Gatchaman-Main,AvatarA,0000,0000,0000,,Even at night, the neighbor \Nhonks the car horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:31.81,Gatchaman-Main,AvatarA,0000,0000,0000,,It's enough to make \Nmy baby seize up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:33.56,Gatchaman-Main,AvatarB,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you should \Nlodge a complaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.63,Gatchaman-Main,AvatarA,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, take legal action?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:37.37,Gatchaman-Main,AvatarA,0000,0000,0000,,But I have no experience \Nin that sort of thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:38.98,Gatchaman-Main,AvatarC,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you ask X?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:41.23,Gatchaman-Main,AvatarA,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:47.32,Gatchaman-X,GeneralX,0000,0000,0000,,What may I help you with?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.51,Gatchaman-Main,Lawyer,0000,0000,0000,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:06:01.34,Gatchaman-Main,Lawyer,0000,0000,0000,,Civil lawsuits aren't \Ntoo much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:02.18,Gatchaman-Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:03.75,Gatchaman-Main,Lawyer,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like,
