Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.33,0:06:07.46,Gatchaman-Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.46,0:06:11.18,Gatchaman-Main,Lawyer,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. First, tell me what's \Nhappening, in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:13.68,Heroes_Sign_Ep03,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not heroes who'll \Nupdate the world.\N{\c&H7DD5EB&}It's us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:13.45,Gatchaman-Main,GirlA,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:15.57,Gatchaman-Main,GirlA,0000,0000,0000,,You're a GALAXter, too, Marippu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:16.70,Gatchaman-Main,GirlB,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like trash (garakuta).
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:18.21,Gatchaman-Main,GirlA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:19.25,Gatchaman-Main,GirlB,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:21.34,Gatchaman-Main,GirlB,0000,0000,0000,,You're asking me if I'm \Na GALAX user, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.66,Gatchaman-Main,GirlB,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:24.15,Gatchaman-Main,GirlA,0000,0000,0000,,It comes in handy, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:26.78,Gatchaman-Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,GALAX is good stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:30.46,Gatchaman-Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,The info you can get \Nfrom the X app is pretty useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:33.03,Gatchaman-Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't that scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.44,0:06:35.29,Gatchaman-Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,There's got to be flame \Nwars and stuff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:36.83,Gatchaman-Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,It's all fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:38.85,Gatchaman-Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,They're good at managing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:42.21,Gatchaman-Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,They match users up in a good way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.06,0:06:45.78,Gatchaman-Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Just give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:48.13,Gatchaman-Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Let's update the world together!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.21,0:06:50.79,Gatchaman-Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:56.93,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:03.32,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Rui.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.78,0:07:06.26,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,Were you able to secure \Na sufficient caloric intake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:07.95,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:09.15,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,Update.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:12.76,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,A balanced diet is very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.40,0:07:16.52,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,Good health is essential \Nfor realizing your ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:19.16,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,Very nice, X.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:21.83,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,You've become good \Nat managing GALAX, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:24.77,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Milord Rui.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:31.13,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.63,Gatchaman-News,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,There has been a noticeable
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:36.97,Gatchaman-News,,0000,0000,0000,,decline in job seekers, \Ngiven the lack of economic recovery
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:40.24,Gatchaman-News,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,and effective policies \Nfor the foreseeable feature.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:44.73,Gatchaman-News,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,In actuality, job seekers appear \Nto be relying, not on agencies,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:46.36,Gatchaman-News,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,but on GALAX.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:50.00,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, it's a problem of matching \Njob seekers with employers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:52.53,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,If they can contact each \Nother directly online,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:55.53,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,why would they need a middle man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:08:00.37,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,Our active users are \Ncontinuing to increase today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:04.43,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,That means the number of people \Nwho resent us will also increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:06.20,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,The more powerful the enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:08.05,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,the more enjoyable \Nthe game, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:16.85,Missing_Persons11:00Ep03v1 - Copy,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Missing Persons Simultaneously Found Across the Nation
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:14.78,Gatchaman-News,A,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm the one who's shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:16.85,Gatchaman-News,A,0000,0000,0000,,When I came to, I was standing \Non my usual way home,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:19.48,Gatchaman-News,A,0000,0000,0000,,but I was told it's been \Nmore than six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:22.66,Gatchaman-News,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Not just this man,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:26.07,Gatchaman-News,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,but others who had gone missing \Nare being found across the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:31.07,Gatchaman-News,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,They all have no memory \Nof the lost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:31.07,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,What, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:33.58,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,Were they abducted by aliens?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:38.37,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:46.79,Prime_minister08-40-Ep03,Sign 1130,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad (667,1)}Prime Minister Resigning
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:42.17,Gatchaman-News,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}This just in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:45.62,Gatchaman-News,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Prime Minister Kamoshida, who had \Nbeen urged to take responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:47.83,Gatchaman-News,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}for his cabinet members' \Nmultiple scandals,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:50.25,Gatchaman-News,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}indicated his intent to resign today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:53.49,Gatchaman-News,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We'll be reporting live from \Nthe prime minister's residence...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:54.88,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,Aww... and this one'd started off \Nwith high approval ratings, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:57.08,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Rui.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:08:58.88,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,Stage clear, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:01.60,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't really a boss character...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:08.62,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,The world's so complicated now \Nthat even excellent leaders
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:11.13,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,might not be enough \Nto turn things around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:14.22,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,Then, who is the true enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:20.87,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it? One of the Hundred?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:23.89,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,An incoming call from Number 26.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:24.98,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,Him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.63,0:09:28.21,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably to ask for \Nusage permission, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:31.38,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I handle him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:33.66,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:36.76,Gatchaman-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste, Rui-Rui.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:40.47,Gatchaman-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Are you being stingy with \Nthat valuable power of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:44.17,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,I did give them power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:47.74,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,the hundred capable GALAXters I chose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:53.61,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,But we'll update the world \Nwithout relying on that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:55.80,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:10:00.16,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to take \Nthat thing along to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:01.70,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:03.75,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,We're the only ones who can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:05.53,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:11.39,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:13.89,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if something's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:17.30,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, he shouldn't have \Ndriven so fast on this road!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:20.29,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,But he may have been \Ndriving a sick person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:23.81,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, maybe his wife \Nwent into sudden labor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:26.70,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you bother \Nthinking about things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:29.83,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,When you think about it that way, \Ndon't you feel like they had a valid reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:32.44,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel less angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:34.81,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:40.74,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,It's more fun this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.78,0:10:50.76,Gatchaman-Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,So, "The current of the \Nflowing river does not cease"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:53.38,Gatchaman-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,might be a phrase even \Nyou guys have heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:58.59,Gatchaman-Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Kamono Choumei was a court \Npoet in his younger years...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:10:57.93,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:00.96,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,There has been a worrisome leak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:04.73,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, there was a power outage \Nat a factory in Tokorozawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:07.56,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,and milk was left at room \Ntemperature for several hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:12.31,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Class is finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:15.24,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,According to the source,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:17.78,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,even though disposal \Nwas recommended,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:19.79,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,the supervisor would not allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:22.11,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, the batch was \Nshipped out after undergoing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:24.04,Gatchaman-X,,0000,0000,0000,,a simple disinfection procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:26.44,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,Is that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:27.38,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:30.80,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,There were factors indicating \Na potential emergency situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:33.00,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,so I illegally obtained data \Non the batch's management
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:36.22,Gatchaman-X,,0000,0000,0000,,and component analysis, \Nand ran an analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:38.21,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,So you did some cracking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.16,0:11:40.97,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:43.05,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,So, are they guilty?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:47.35,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:50.27,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.55,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:11:59.15,Gatchaman-Main,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:02.74,Gatchaman-Main,Hosaka,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:02.30,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:04.01,Gatchaman-Main,Watanabe,0000,0000,0000,,It's from X.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:05.44,Gatchaman-Main,Watanabe,0000,0000,0000,,The milk's not safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:06.91,Gatchaman-Main,Hosaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:08.94,Gatchaman-Main,Hosaka,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:10.95,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,It's urgent, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.22,0:12:13.46,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! Help us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:22.83,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,We got to the kiosk lady okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:24.89,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Next, a school-wide announcement \Nand then hit the vending machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:27.93,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Split up and unplug them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:29.33,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.33,0:12:31.09,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get permission \Nfrom the teachers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.09,0:12:32.83,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:36.49,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard about the milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:38.68,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:42.11,Gatchaman-Main,Utsutsu,0000,0000,0000,,I feel dreamy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.21,0:12:48.41,Gatchaman-Main,Chiba,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:51.41,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,It's an anti-tampering device.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.14,0:12:55.21,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no announcement yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:57.28,Gatchaman-Main,Ariga,0000,0000,0000,,They won't let us in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:13:00.46,Gatchaman-Main,Ariga,0000,0000,0000,,The broadcast room is only \Naccessible from the teachers' lounge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:03.14,Gatchaman-Main,Yamamura,0000,0000,0000,,So, we need to tell everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:05.20,Gatchaman-Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a ruse?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:07.47,Gatchaman-Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just take stuff \Nfrom the internet at face value.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:11.58,Gatchaman-Main,Koyamauchi,0000,0000,0000,,But there are lots of people \Nwho've been helped by GALAX.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:14.81,Gatchaman-Main,Tanaka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, X tells us everything, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:18.68,Gatchaman-Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not be using it to cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.68,0:13:20.75,Gatchaman-Main,Yamamura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, c'mon! That's not why we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:21.28,Gatchaman-Main,Fujio,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:23.86,Gatchaman-Main,Fujio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm using GALAX, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:26.23,Gatchaman-Main,Fujio,0000,0000,0000,,and I think it can be trusted...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:28.14,Gatchaman-Main,TeacherB,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we can, \Nat least, urge caution...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:30.41,Gatchaman-Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we should \Nconsult the principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.26,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Consult?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:33.83,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.11,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the key \Nto the vending machines?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:36.43,Gatchaman-Main,Ariga,0000,0000,0000,,That's also in the teachers' lounge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:38.08,Gatchaman-Main,Ariga,0000,0000,0000,,They say we need permission...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:41.43,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send a decoy. \NLet's use this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:43.71,Gatchaman-Main,Ariga,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's kind of like a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:44.92,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,A decoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.52,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,You, of course, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.52,0:13:48.50,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Use your sword and mess around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:50.27,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:51.93,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,You can use an umbrella \Nor whatever, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:53.67,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Get the attention \Nof people who are getting
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.67,0:13:56.12,Gatchaman-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,in the way at the teachers' lounge\Nand in front of the broadcast room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:57.39,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:59.27,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, what about \Nmy reputation at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:01.36,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, you're a Gatchaman, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:04.53,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:06.80,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,The school's in a crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.80,0:14:10.18,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,But that's no excuse to skulk \Naround and go out of control!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:12.37,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes should face \Nproblems head-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:14.20,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:16.16,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,It's like that car \Nearlier this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:19.42,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,That car wasn't \Nout of control for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:22.81,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you don't know \Nif there really was a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:24.61,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,That's just your speculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:27.05,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,But now, we definitely have a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.58,0:14:29.49,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,You're a hero, right, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:32.97,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,We have to protect everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:41.18,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.18,0:14:42.44,Gatchaman-Main,Yamamura,0000,0000,0000,,O-Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:43.94,Gatchaman-Main,Yamamura,0000,0000,0000,,The key to the vending machines\Nis probably there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:15:02.00,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drink the milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:05.93,Gatchaman-Main,Kawano,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:06.75,Gatchaman-Main,Kawano,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:10.88,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still using the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:12.65,Gatchaman-Main,Ariga,0000,0000,0000,,They're in front of the \Ninner courtyard now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:15.11,Gatchaman-Main,Ariga,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:16.95,Gatchaman-Main,Ariga,0000,0000,0000,,This one's the last of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:18.47,Gatchaman-Main,Yamamura,0000,0000,0000,,What now? Should we go get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:21.31,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:23.77,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Can you slash right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:24.73,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Slash?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:25.98,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:27.43,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:28.69,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:36.99,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,I slashed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:39.97,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.07,0:15:43.17,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,The world has been updated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:44.92,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Mission complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:48.05,Gatchaman-Main,Everyone,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, updated!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:57.23,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,Nationwide, 68% percent of schools
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:59.28,Gatchaman-X,,0000,0000,0000,,and 74% of businesses \Naverted any casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:06.02,Background_Sign_Bottom-Ep03,Sign 2049,0000,0000,0000,,Flaw in Quality Control at Dairy Company
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:02.73,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Victims who made purchases \Nfrom individual stores
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:06.02,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}and wholesale distributors \Nnumber in the double digits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:09.15,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,That's more than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:11.64,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,Is that an indication \Nof just how many
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.64,0:16:13.48,Gatchaman-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,people still don't trust \Ninformation from GALAX?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:16.56,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,It is true that people \Nof a certain age range
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:20.37,Gatchaman-X,,0000,0000,0000,,or in certain professions \Nexhibit markedly lower confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:24.06,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,However, many who \Nacknowledged the information
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:27.46,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,were still unable to take \Nappropriate action.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:30.34,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:33.40,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,They're afraid of being held \Nresponsible in the aftermath,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:36.64,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,so they cannot easily take action \Nbased on outside information.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:40.16,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,It's what people call the adverse \Neffects of a vertical society.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:44.66,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably what we're \Nactually up against.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:50.07,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,Running GALAX has made \Nmy enemies clearer than ever to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:53.87,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,They're the ones who refuse \Nto see people as individuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.27,0:16:56.08,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who cannot see the joy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:59.61,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,in helping others if there is no \Nreward or reputation to be gained.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:01.58,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,Either way,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:04.87,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,anyone who's not... fun, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:12.97,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was great, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:16.09,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,You looked kind of cute \Nbeing scolded by the teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:18.51,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your attempt \Nto make me feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:20.47,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you wanted me to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.28,0:17:22.49,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.59,0:17:25.75,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,But, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.16,0:17:30.12,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,This kind of... the internet's \Ngot a lot going for it, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:31.87,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:34.82,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Its influence is huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:36.60,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:37.41,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:40.95,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,If your battery runs out, \Nor if you don't have a signal, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:44.15,Gatchaman-Main,Hajime,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just blindly \Nfollow the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:45.46,Gatchaman-Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:17:57.30,Gatchaman-Main,Utsutsu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it, Al-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:18:01.01,Gatchaman-Main,Utsutsu,0000,0000,0000,,Stop. It tickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:02.66,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,It's dinner time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:04.51,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Come help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:05.64,Gatchaman-Main,Utsutsu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:07.91,Gatchaman-Main,Utsutsu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:11.92,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.47,0:18:13.43,Gatchaman-Main,Utsutsu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:17.97,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Is that from Hajime-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:22.06,Gatchaman-Main,Utsutsu,0000,0000,0000,,She just pushed it on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:24.66,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,That girl's way too fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:26.51,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you become friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:33.88,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:40.00,Gatchaman-Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,All right, beans are \Non the menu today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.44,0:18:42.99,Gatchaman-Main,Utsutsu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dreamy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:50.27,Gatchaman-Main,Photog,0000,0000,0000,,Can you circle around \Nand get closer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:52.25,Gatchaman-Main,Photog,0000,0000,0000,,I want the setting sun \Nin the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:19:00.53,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,Multiple rescue requests \Nhave appeared on the timeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:03.51,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,A news channel helicopter has crashed \Ninto a ropeway's support pillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:07.37,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,The pillars bent, stranding \Nthe two gondolas on either side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:10.96,Gatchaman-Main,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,You brought that to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.96,Gatchaman-Main,Kudou,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Toyosaki, \Nthe gym teacher, annoying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:15.35,Gatchaman-Main,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't mean you should—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:18.92,Gatchaman-Main,Kudou,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not like I'm going \Nto do anything to him with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:25.58,Gatchaman-Main,Kudou,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.33,0:19:57.13,Gatchaman-Main,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.47,0:19:59.21,Gatchaman-Main,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:00.72,Gatchaman-Main,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,Stop resisting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:01.74,Gatchaman-Main,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:07.40,Gatchaman-Main,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:08.47,Gatchaman-Main,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he? Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:09.93,Gatchaman-Main,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,Look around!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.30,0:20:12.51,Gatchaman-Main,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:14.44,Gatchaman-Main,Kudou,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:15.38,Gatchaman-Main,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,Stop resisting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:15.38,Gatchaman-Main,Kudou,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:16.57,Gatchaman-Main,Kudou,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.57,0:20:17.61,Gatchaman-Main,Kudou,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:23.19,Gatchaman-Main,Katze,0000,0000,0000,,Gatcha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:29.58,Gatchaman-Main,Jou,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:31.81,Gatchaman-Main,Jou,0000,0000,0000,,Was that your doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.81,0:20:35.83,Gatchaman-Main,Katze,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:37.84,Gatchaman-Main,Jou,0000,0000,0000,,Go...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:45.56,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,Number 58 of the Hundred \Nis on the dispatched rescue team.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:48.23,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,They are in operation,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.23,0:20:50.31,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,but due to numerous obstacles \Nthat cannot be overcome,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:52.53,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,he is requesting usage permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:55.21,Gatchaman-Main,100-A,0000,0000,0000,,There are several GALAXters among
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:56.39,Gatchaman-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,the passengers exchanging information,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.39,0:20:58.36,Gatchaman-Main,100-A,0000,0000,0000,,but the situation seems pretty dire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:20:59.98,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:05.01,Gatchaman-Main,100-B,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't use {\i1}it{\i0} now, when else?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:07.37,Gatchaman-Main,100-B,0000,0000,0000,,The rescue team alone would \Njust end in a fail game.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:10.62,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,I simulated all possible avenues \Nfor a successful rescue
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:13.83,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,given the current available \Nhuman resources,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:15.56,Gatchaman-X,X,0000,0000,0000,,but all results were negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.30,0:21:19.75,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll have to use...\Nthe Crowds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:40.02,Gatchaman-Main,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\fad(400,1)}Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:42.53,Gatchaman-Main,Rui,0000,0000,0000,,Play the Game...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
